title: Chelsea Handler / Cannabis & Ayahuasca
description: Sean goes deep to update Dr. Wali on how his colonoscopy went. Then they confront the importance of being honest in therapy. Chelsea Handler rhapsodizes about her love of cannabis and her experience with ayahuasca.
